<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10701</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>14702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利跟着那个女人进了她的小屋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>14702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很紧张，但那个女人看上去好像很好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21702</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小屋里有一张床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他还看到一个大箱子，里面装有谷物和铜锅。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32451</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>墙上挂着神像和一块高高的玻璃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当毛克利走到玻璃前，他吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“另一个男孩儿住在这里！”他惊奇地想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48209</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他举起一只胳膊，玻璃里的男孩儿也举起一只胳膊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48209</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利动了动手指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男孩儿又一次做了毛克利正在做的动作。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她指了指毛克利，又指了指镜子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”终于，毛克利明白了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“ 玻璃里的男孩儿是我！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人给了他一些牛奶和面包。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她把手放在他的头上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“拿图？你还记得我给你的鞋吗？ ”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利摇了摇头，听不懂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人摸了摸他的脚，感觉像动物的角一样硬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。”她悲伤地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这双脚从来没穿过鞋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102303</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但你看起来像我的拿图，你将是我的儿子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利以前从来没在屋顶下呆过。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他爬上凳子去摸屋顶上的稻草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小屋有一个门和一扇窗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122552</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果他觉得自己被困住了，他也会撕了屋顶的稻草。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这想法让他心里感觉舒服一些。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但还有别的事情困扰着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须学人类的语言。”他意识到，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我不理解他们的话，我就不能和他们一起生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以麦苏雅每说一句话，毛克利就重复一遍。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天黑以前，他学会了小屋里许多东西的名字。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>睡觉前，麦苏雅和丈夫关上了小屋的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利感到被困住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169668</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他飞快地从窗子溜走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须把他带回来！”麦苏雅说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她丈夫拦住了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187775</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别管他。”他说，“这个男孩儿以前从来没睡过床。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果他真是我们的儿子，他不会逃跑的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利跑到田边，在高高的草丛里躺了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200834</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204335</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他快要闭上眼睛时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204335</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个灰色的、软软的鼻子碰了他一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215084</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“格瑞布拉德！”毛克利高兴地大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215084</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>狼闻了闻毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呃！”狼说，“跟着你来是一个最糟糕的奖励。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你闻起来有木头的烟味和牛味——人类的味！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利笑了。“一切都好吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不太好。”格瑞布拉德回答道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有谢尔坎的消息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他出去打猎了一阵子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，那红花把他烧得很厉害。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他发誓回来时要把你抓回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251734</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想把你的骨头放在河里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他吓不到我。”毛克利说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“总有一天，我会抓住他的！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>连狼妈妈也说这是事实。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德看上去很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274986</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢尔坎很危险，毛克利，你要小心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274986</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会小心的。”毛克利打了个哈欠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今晚我太累了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天我学到了很多新东西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>下次再告诉我更多的新消息吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他闭上了一会儿眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不会忘记你是一只狼吧？”格瑞布拉德急切地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302985</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“绝不会的。”毛克利保证道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302985</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306988</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会永远记住我爱你和我们的洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306988</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309735</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，你一定要记住一些事情，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>格瑞布拉德，是狼群赶走了我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那群人也会赶走你的。”格瑞布拉德说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>319235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322234</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人只是人，毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322234</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们谈话就像池塘里青蛙们聊天，没什么意义。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>330037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>330037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>332085</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又闭上了眼睛。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>332085</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好好睡吧！”格瑞布拉德最后说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336585</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>338606</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我几个星期后再来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>338606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>344885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到竹林里找我，竹林在人类田地边上。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>344885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>351574</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。”毛克利小声说，“晚安。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>